                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On September 23, Nikola Petkov was executed in Sofia. In a statement issued to
                    the press that same day, the Department of State described the efforts of the
                    United States to obtain a review of the Petkov case and denounced the trial and
                    execution as a travesty of justice. For the text of the statement, see
                    Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, October 5, 1947, page
                    702.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
